{"surah":95,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"95:1","arabic":"وَٱلتِّينِ وَٱلزَّيْتُونِ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"By the fig and the olive","id":"Demi (buah) Tin dan (buah) Zaitun,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلتِّينِ","en":"By the fig","id":"demi tin"},{"a":"وَٱلزَّيْتُونِ","en":"and the olive","id":"dan zaitun"}]},{"n":2,"key":"95:2","arabic":"وَطُورِ سِينِينَ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] Mount Sinai","id":"demi gunung Sinai,","words":[{"a":"وَطُورِ","en":"And (the) Mount","id":"dan bukit"},{"a":"سِينِينَ","en":"Sinai","id":"Sinai"}]},{"n":3,"key":"95:3","arabic":"وَهَـٰذَا ٱلْبَلَدِ ٱلْأَمِينِ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] this secure city [i.e., Makkah],","id":"dan demi negeri (Mekkah) yang aman ini.","words":[{"a":"وَهَـٰذَا","en":"And this","id":"dan ini"},{"a":"ٱلْبَلَدِ","en":"[the] city","id":"negri"},{"a":"ٱلْأَمِينِ","en":"[the] secure","id":"aman"}]},{"n":4,"key":"95:4","arabic":"لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ فِىٓ أَحْسَنِ تَقْوِيمٍ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"We have certainly created man in the best of stature;","id":"Sungguh, Kami telah menciptakan manusia dalam bentuk yang sebaik-baiknya,","words":[{"a":"لَقَدْ","en":"Indeed","id":"sesungguhnya"},{"a":"خَلَقْنَا","en":"We created","id":"Kami telah menciptakan"},{"a":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","en":"man","id":"manusia"},{"a":"فِىٓ","en":"in","id":"dalam"},{"a":"أَحْسَنِ","en":"(the) best","id":"sebaik-baik"},{"a":"تَقْوِيمٍۢ","en":"mould","id":"bentuk"}]},{"n":5,"key":"95:5","arabic":"ثُمَّ رَدَدْنَـٰهُ أَسْفَلَ سَـٰفِلِينَ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"Then We return him to the lowest of the low,","id":"kemudian Kami kembalikan dia ke tempat yang serendah-rendahnya,","words":[{"a":"ثُمَّ","en":"Then","id":"kemudian"},{"a":"رَدَدْنَـٰهُ","en":"We returned him","id":"Kami kembalikan"},{"a":"أَسْفَلَ","en":"(to the) lowest","id":"lebih rendah/paling rendah"},{"a":"سَـٰفِلِينَ","en":"(of the) low","id":"tempat yang rendah"}]},{"n":6,"key":"95:6","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ فَلَهُمْ أَجْرٌ غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"Except for those who believe and do righteous deeds, for they will have a reward uninterrupted.","id":"kecuali orang-orang yang beriman dan mengerjakan kebajikan; maka mereka akan mendapat pahala yang tidak ada putus-putusnya.","words":[{"a":"إِلَّا","en":"Except","id":"kecuali"},{"a":"ٱلَّذِينَ","en":"those who","id":"orang-orang yang"},{"a":"ءَامَنُوا۟","en":"believe","id":"beriman"},{"a":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","en":"and do","id":"dan mereka berbuat/beramal"},{"a":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","en":"righteous deeds","id":"kebajikan/saleh"},{"a":"فَلَهُمْ","en":"then for them","id":"maka bagi mereka"},{"a":"أَجْرٌ","en":"(is a) reward","id":"pahala"},{"a":"غَيْرُ","en":"never","id":"bukan/tidak"},{"a":"مَمْنُونٍۢ","en":"ending","id":"terputus"}]},{"n":7,"key":"95:7","arabic":"فَمَا يُكَذِّبُكَ بَعْدُ بِٱلدِّينِ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"So what yet causes you to deny the Recompense?","id":"Maka apa yang menyebabkan (mereka) mendustakanmu (tentang) hari pembalasan setelah (adanya keterangan-keterangan) itu?","words":[{"a":"فَمَا","en":"Then what","id":"maka apakah"},{"a":"يُكَذِّبُكَ","en":"causes you to deny","id":"mendustakanmu"},{"a":"بَعْدُ","en":"after (this)","id":"sesudah"},{"a":"بِٱلدِّينِ","en":"the judgment","id":"hari pembalasan/agama"}]},{"n":8,"key":"95:8","arabic":"أَلَيْسَ ٱللَّهُ بِأَحْكَمِ ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ","page":597,"juz":30,"en":"Is not Allāh the most just of judges?","id":"Bukankah Allah Hakim yang paling adil?","words":[{"a":"أَلَيْسَ","en":"Is not","id":"bukankah"},{"a":"ٱللَّهُ","en":"Allah","id":"Allah"},{"a":"بِأَحْكَمِ","en":"(the) Most Just","id":"lebih bijaksana/seadil-adilnya"},{"a":"ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ","en":"(of) the Judges","id":"para hakim"}]}]}